msgstr "Scorri fino alla sezione :guilabel:`E-commerce`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:35
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Configure Delivery Methods`, click :icon:`fa-arrow-"
