#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:44
msgid ""
"The :ref:`shipping price <inventory/shipping/calculate-delivery-cost>`, "
"including the :guilabel:`Margin on rate` or :guilabel:`Additional margin` "
